## Test Coverage Requirements

**Minimum Coverage Targets:**
- **Core financial logic:** 100% coverage (scripts/core/)
- **Workflows:** 80% coverage (scripts/workflows/)
- **Integrations:** 60% coverage (scripts/integrations/)

**Measure Coverage:**
```bash
pytest --cov=scripts --cov-report=html tests/
open htmlcov/index.html
```

**Coverage Exceptions:**
- Main blocks (`if __name__ == "__main__"`)
- Type checking blocks (`if TYPE_CHECKING`)
- Debugging code (temporary print statements)

